                <ParagraphSentence>
                  <Sentence WritingMode="vertical">銷却ノ為ニスル国債証券ノ買入ハ随意契約ヲ以テ之ヲ為スコトヲ得</Sentence>
                </ParagraphSentence>
              </Paragraph>
            </Article>
